Identify Event Monitoring Analytics App User Types

The Event Monitoring Analytics Apps license includes permissions required by users to administer Event Monitoring Analytics and explore event data. Set up Event Monitoring Analytics by considering different ways people access features, categorizing users into types.

Users view Event Monitoring Analytics dashboards and datasets.
Administrators or managers create apps, dashboards, and datasets, customize the app experience.

Create two basic permission sets: "view" for most users, and "manage" for administrators and managers.
